Halo Innovations Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback























halo innovations inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Apparel & Textile Products
Sub-Industry: Apparel, Footwear & Acc Design
Halo Innovations, Inc. develops sleeping products. The Company manufactures sleeping blankets, swaddles, night knits, changing pad covers, crib sets, and diaper covers. Halo Innovations operates in the State of Minnesota.




