HALO innovations, inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 3:03 AM ET
Textiles, Apparel and Luxury Goods

Company Overview of HALO innovations, inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
HALO innovations, inc. develops safe sleeping environment products for adults and children. The company offers crib sets, swaddles, wearable blankets, gift sets, collections, sensitive skin sleepwear, clothing with moisture-wicking, and mattress filters and accessories. It offers products online and through retailers in the United States and Canada. The company was founded in 1994 and is based in Minnetonka, Minnesota. As of December 12, 2016, HALO innovations, inc. operates as a subsidiary of Aden & Anais, Inc.


111 Cheshire LaneSuite 700Minnetonka, MN 55305United StatesFounded in 1994



Phone: 952-259-1500

Fax: 952-278-1000

www.halosleep.com







