HALO Innovations, Inc. HALO SleepSack Pink Kitty Spots Wearable Blanket MicrofleeceBy HALO INNOVATIONS, INC.Product Details
    HALO SleepSack Pink Kitty Dots Microfleece Wearable Blanket: Use over regular sleepwear to take the place of loose blankets Unzips from the bottom for easy diaper changes Generous sack design allows room for kicking, but cannot be kicked off so baby stays warm all night Sleeveless design reduces the risk of overheating Used by hundreds hospital nurseries nationwide as their product of choice for teaching parents safe sleep practices Recognized as "Hip Healthy" by the International Hip Dysplasia Institute "Back is Best" embroidery reminds caregivers to place baby on his or her back HALO supports non-profit organizations like First Candle/SIDS Alliance and The Canadian Foundation for the Study of Infant Deaths 100 percent polyester microfleece Machine wash warm with like colors; do not bleach; tumble dry low Size preemie fits birth-5 lbs Size small fits 10-18 lbs Size medium fits 16-24 lbs Size large fits 22-28 lbs Size extra large fits 26-36 lbs Questions about product recalls? Items that are a part of a recall are removed from the Walmart.com site, and are no longer available for purchase. These items include Walmart.com items only, not those of Marketplace sellers. Customers who have purchased a recalled item will be notified by email or by letter sent to the address given at the time of purchase. For complete recall information, go to Walmart Recalls.





